The paper deals with information extraction from images of documents using deep neural networks and deductive reasoning. This falls under the domains of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of logic programs and meta-interpretive learning also suggests a connection to natural language processing (cs.CL) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
